OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlack activist and         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fperformer awarded purple   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fplaque                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A purple plaque which celebrates the   
OL,6, lives of women in Wales is being given 
OL,7, to a black woman for the first time.   
OL,9,FActivist and performer Patti Flynn's   
OL,10,Fachievements included securing a       
OL,11,Fmemorial for black soldiers after a    
OL,12,F26-year campaign.                      
OL,14,FMichael Flynn welcomed the award for   
OL,15,Fhis mother, who died in 2020, saying   
OL,16,Fshe "stood on the shoulders of other   
OL,17,Fstrong, black women".                  
OL,19,FThe plaque will be unveiled later at   
OL,20,Fthe Wales Millennium Centre in Cardiff.
